Testing
Test Case 1: "research innovation"
•	Query: Multi-word query about research and innovation
•	Expected: Passages mentioning research activities
•	Result:  Returns 3 relevant passages from pages 26, 6, and 5
Test Case 2: "gradient descent optimization"
•	Query: Technical terms from ML/optimization
•	Expected: Returns passages about optimization techniques
•	Result: Returns relevant technical passages
Design Decisions
Why Python Integration?
•	Mojo 0.25.7 has compatibility issues with complex struct types
•	Python provides robust PDF processing (PyPDF2)
•	Python's regex and math libraries are well-tested
•	Allows focus on algorithm implementation rather than type system issues
Why This TF-IDF Formula?
•	Logarithmic TF: Prevents term frequency from dominating scores
•	IDF weighting: Ensures rare, specific terms matter more
•	Length normalization: √length provides balanced normalization (not too aggressive)

